==German==
===Etymology===
From {{OHG.}} ''zwibollo'', which is a redefinition of {{OHG.}} ''zibollo''; from Middle Latin ''caepola'', ''cipola'', a diminutive form of Latin ''[[cepa]]''.
===Noun===
'''Zwiebel''' {{f}} (''pl'' Zwiebeln)
# [[onion]]
# [[bulb]] (of a plant)

